{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"37f3fd4a5e","title":"中共中央关于土改后秋田收获物分配问题给中南局的批复","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"de20e0e3ab","index":0,"year":1950,"month":6,"day":22,"articleId":"37f3fd4a5e"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e818add651","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于土改后秋田收获物分配问题给中南局的批复","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"37f3fd4a5e"},{"id":"10af4f7ec6","type":"appellation","text":"中南局：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"37f3fd4a5e"},{"id":"83dc08b47e","type":"paragraph","text":"辰艳电悉。关于秋田收获物分配问题，我们认为：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"37f3fd4a5e"},{"id":"831fa61b85","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）应确实执行谁种谁收的规定，不分青苗，土地分配后一般应仍由原耕者继续经营，加工施肥，而于收割后，由原耕者以收获物之三成给新分地户，作为使用土地之报酬。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"37f3fd4a5e"},{"id":"d028dc21e5","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）如土地分配给新分地户后，原耕者不愿或无力继续经营时，则由农会会同原耕者和新分地户共同商定，由新分地户经营，并视原耕者由耕犁下种直到分地时所有的经营耗费之多寡，商定于秋收后分给原耕者以收获物之三成到四成作为报酬。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"37f3fd4a5e"},{"id":"3e0a478a06","type":"paragraph","text":" 中  央巳  养","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"37f3fd4a5e"}],"page":{"id":"2d90acde5a","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"37f3fd4a5e","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}